BORDERS -- POLAND; GERMANY -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- POLAND; POLAND -- SECURITY; 
USSR -- FOREIGN RELATIONS -- WEST GERMANY 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
