CALIFORNIA; CALIFORNIA -- POLITICS; CALIFORNIA -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; 
HOSPITALS -- CALIFORNIA; NURSING HOMES; MEDI CAL; HEALTH WORKERS 
</P>
