CASUALTIES; SEARCH AND RESCUE 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA071890-0082 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 248881 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 18, 1990, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 12; Column 1; National Desk 
</P>
