<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY EARNINGS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Provena Foods Inc.: The Santa Ana specialty food-processing and distributing 
company reported net income of $196,223 for the second quarter, contrasted with 
a loss of $68,439 for the period last year. Sales jumped 30% to $10.5 million 
from $8.1 million. Net income for the first half of the year more than tripled 
to $395,028, and sales rose 26% to $19.9 million from $15.8 million. 
</P>
